# CL-3: Data Privacy
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All sensitive data handling

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Sensitive Data: Information requiring confidentiality or protection under law or policy.

ENFORCE: Sensitive data must be encrypted at rest and in transit; access controls must enforce least privilege; logs must never contain PII.
PROHIBIT: Storing sensitive data without encryption; sharing without authorization; PII in logs or config files.
ON VIOLATION: Halt skill execution → notify orchestrator and Security Skill.
